Want to get your first wholesale deal or be coached by me and my team in real estate? Tap the link in my bio to sign up 🔥

Congratulations to my brother @ralphdiesel for completing his first fix and flip! 👏🏼 Most people who get into the business make only 10-15% margin per deal, but Ralph is starting off with high standards 🔥 

If you want to find deals with high margin just like how my students are, build long term wealth and create freedom, option and choice, tap the link in my bio to learn more about my Mentorship program and see if you’re a good fit. Let’s goooo 🔥🔥🔥

node.text:
Congrats @destinationdreamhomes 👏🏼👏🏼👏🏼 for completing your first wholesale deal of $25,000! DeAnna is a Realtor listing homes and recently she had an unfortunate event and broke her leg. But that didn’t stop her from finding a deal 🏘💸 happy for you DeAnna!

Tap the link in my bio to learn more about real estate mentorship!

#realestate #realestateinvesting #realestateinvestor #realtor #realestateagent #realestatebroker #wholesalingrealestate #wealth

node.text:
Congrats to @thejesusmejia for buying his FIRST BRRRR Rental property!! He’s one of many students who have successfully purchase an investment this year and he’s been chipping away and take action on a daily basis 👏🏼

If you want to become one of my students and learn how to find great margin deals, evaluate them and know how I communicate with sellers, tap the link in my bio to watch a free training, schedule a call with my team to see if you’re a good fit for the program. Let’s go 🔥

#realestate #realestateinvesting #realestateinvestor #rentalproperty #incomeproperty #investmentproperty
